  "chunks": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "Ollama just shipped Claude Desktop support.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9433d07bc0e5da7f5c95bf9e884cffa43647118bf6dfea55e39ed798d3ac98c7",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 2.3219954648526078,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "The launch tweet exploded. 139 thousand views in hours.",
      "checksum": "sha256:456b0528b7fd89a96af403de39e1c38038822430b36d77e241bf814c7652023f",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 3.7151927437641725,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 6
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "Here is what just unlocked. The Claude desktop app, with any Ollama Cloud model.",
      "checksum": "sha256:abca263eb0b69b028bb0498185a1b7c45a2ca6c56b5fca44e1bf7c5c9bfe4a72",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 4.73687074829932,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 15
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "Open source models, frontier scale parameter counts, all running through Anthropic's interface.",
      "checksum": "sha256:14692f68736e4f1bf7bd693ccb6b5d5208ebe2f33ffd2c816b814a4ef58c31b8",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 5.340589569160998,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 29
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "First, export your Ollama API key. Then run, ollama launch claude-desktop.",
      "checksum": "sha256:72a26783c396e39725bdca30f9ef9954a6c2e10fd5f0ebcc69d24522178ac6ec",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 5.015510204081632,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 41
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "Reload the app and the model picker now shows Ollama models.",
      "checksum": "sha256:aea22bc1e607887ab4c1cebd246d2aac4bf063a57a8759d6535343fdd8aa759a",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 3.297233560090703,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 52
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "Switch to Claude Cowork. Pick a model from the dropdown.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c67ebccb7af9d87557e5e656cade1f068bdb6e57ac0068b8feaefd57373ca4dd",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 3.01859410430839,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 63
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "Let it handle real work, autonomously. Organizing files, talking to your local apps.",
      "checksum": "sha256:4690f2f7392ddf543ea4658b858013a5182ef208a858a27e94fa8fd911a0547f",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 5.015510204081632,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 73
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "Agentic tasks with the model you chose. Same thing in Claude Code.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3fb50dc52db1d7a570c7430e9b67e29291449efd11ef595b30a4a1fa596709ce",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 4.133151927437642,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 86
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "Same dropdown. Same Ollama Cloud lineup.",
      "checksum": "sha256:7191f77273abada9f798297a0873459aef495e97c7e07888de97e9667d5d0c60",
      "wav": "chunk-09.wav",
      "duration": 2.3219954648526078,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 98
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "The launch demo shipped a snake game graphics upgrade plan, running on Kimi.",
      "checksum": "sha256:88dbce010250e3081b1b8f57acfd0d5488f6529809acc0dea89a7a3d8be54eb9",
      "wav": "chunk-10.wav",
      "duration": 4.133151927437642,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 104
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "The lineup is deep. Kimi. GPT-OSS. Qwen.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a6c1e5ee2aa2a71b036dbb03f86d5249934cff88fd1f2de9e2830c1abbad7469",
      "wav": "chunk-11.wav",
      "duration": 2.972154195011338,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 117
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "Plus Devstral, Ministral, GLM, and Minimax.",
      "checksum": "sha256:21af88b72bf200d22b22ec9af5641d14dfee15d9d4e19e81c85151d433d03060",
      "wav": "chunk-12.wav",
      "duration": 2.647074829931973,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 124
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "text": "Everything in Ollama Cloud, discovered automatically.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5686ac1f1c36b65e2c0c7dad5aa6aa065464333a747bb24ea0234341e7de35e3",
      "wav": "chunk-13.wav",
      "duration": 2.9257142857142857,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 130
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "text": "Two limits to know. Web search is not supported yet.",
      "checksum": "sha256:53eaa92babc4ac753cc4fd22d7166b15f1ea9a65a829471d34e5f853dc48139c",
      "wav": "chunk-14.wav",
      "duration": 2.8792743764172335,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 136
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "text": "Extensions are not supported yet. Subagents inherit your current model.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ec3062ea8078f6f338eb0231ff5c9e7a29f789e5efdef709487e01abde2d7a9a",
      "wav": "chunk-15.wav",
      "duration": 4.133151927437642,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 146
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "text": "Full setup walkthrough is at docs.ollama.com slash integrations slash claude-desktop.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0efc1a15c047b03a542f88cbb776e335372a7a0dda44a1319900281dba7c46b5",
      "wav": "chunk-16.wav",
      "duration": 4.6439909297052155,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 156
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "text": "Join the Dynamous AI community to learn AI and build your own second brain.",
      "checksum": "sha256:fb653f21bda5a06085f9b6c7d23becd2fa7f3b83254cdbc5c981cab4da4d060e",
      "wav": "chunk-17.wav",
      "duration": 4.08671201814059,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 166
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "text": "10 percent off in the pinned comment.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ab6d54c5c14114da7941163413a025332f2f291719e51ee3ef0fe57593d7ee03",
      "wav": "chunk-18.wav",
      "duration": 2.043356009070295,
